plot: When a familiar foe descends upon Gotham, Batwoman and Mary find they must rely on each other more than ever; Alice has a new mission and gets an unexpected ally to join her.

Batwoman and Mary come up with a plan to get Alice back from Safiyah. , Luke goes after Russel and meets John Diggle, who is visiting Gotham for reasons of his own. Meanwhile, Kate begins to regain her memories and turns to Roman for answers.—Gislef
